  "detailed_description": "<strong>OCTOPTICOM</strong> is an open-ended puzzle programming game about designing and optimizing optical computing devices. Use lasers, mirrors, filters and other components to read, transform and write sequences of colored squares. Solve a variety of light puzzles and find clever ways to make your solutions elegant and compact.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/943190/extras/e0aca3182c7f3c0a6e3456d743011c23.poster.avif?t=1758356195\" width=588 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/943190/extras/e0aca3182c7f3c0a6e3456d743011c23.webm?t=1758356195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/943190/extras/e0aca3182c7f3c0a6e3456d743011c23.mp4?t=1758356195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Lasers</li><li>8 colors</li><li>A lot of squares</li><li>More than 40 levels of light programming</li><li>Not a single line of assembly code required</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/943190/extras/fe6918b87fc19579d9f98586ab615f5d.poster.avif?t=1758356195\" width=592 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/943190/extras/fe6918b87fc19579d9f98586ab615f5d.webm?t=1758356195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/943190/extras/fe6918b87fc19579d9f98586ab615f5d.mp4?t=1758356195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>OCTOPTICOM</strong> is an open-ended puzzle programming game about designing and optimizing optical computing devices. Use lasers, mirrors, filters and other components to read, transform and write sequences of colored squares. Solve a variety of light puzzles and find clever ways to make your solutions elegant and compact.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/943190/extras/e0aca3182c7f3c0a6e3456d743011c23.poster.avif?t=1758356195\" width=588 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/943190/extras/e0aca3182c7f3c0a6e3456d743011c23.webm?t=1758356195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/943190/extras/e0aca3182c7f3c0a6e3456d743011c23.mp4?t=1758356195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Lasers</li><li>8 colors</li><li>A lot of squares</li><li>More than 40 levels of light programming</li><li>Not a single line of assembly code required</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/943190/extras/fe6918b87fc19579d9f98586ab615f5d.poster.avif?t=1758356195\" width=592 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/943190/extras/fe6918b87fc19579d9f98586ab615f5d.webm?t=1758356195\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/943190/extras/fe6918b87fc19579d9f98586ab615f5d.mp4?t=1758356195\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
